Package: aboveR
Title: LiDAR Terrain Analysis and Change Detection from Above
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Chris", "Lyons", , "chris@nullislandlabs.dev",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Terrain change detection, cut and fill volume estimation, terrain profiling, reclamation monitoring, erosion analysis, and flood risk assessment from LiDAR point clouds and DEMs. Built on 'lidR' for point cloud I/O and 'terra' for raster operations. Includes access utilities for 'KyFromAbove' cloud-native elevation data on AWS.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/null-island-labs/aboveR
BugReports: https://github.com/null-island-labs/aboveR/issues
